@startuml

actor NailMaster
participant "Staff Portal" as StaffPortal
participant "Backend API" as Backend

NailMaster -> StaffPortal: Access Service Catalog
StaffPortal -> Backend: Request My Services
Backend -> StaffPortal: Display Services
StaffPortal -> NailMaster: Show Service List

NailMaster -> StaffPortal: Update Service Price
StaffPortal -> Backend: Update Service Request
Backend -> Backend: Update Service Record
note right of Backend
  Price updated successfully
  New price effective immediately
end note
Backend -> StaffPortal: 200 Success
StaffPortal -> NailMaster: Service Updated

@enduml
